  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dca\u0db4\u0ddd\u0da7\u0dca \u0d91\u0d9a\u0dca\u0daf\u0dd2\u0db1 \u0dc3\u0dda\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dc0 \u0dc3\u0db3\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0da7 \u0dad\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dca\u0d9a \u0dad\u0dd4\u0db1\u0d9a",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Passport one-day service in three more districts from Monday",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Investment Promotion Minister Dhammika Perera said that the one-day passport service will be started in three more districts from next Monday.",
        "In a program held in Colombo yesterday, he stated that accordingly, this service will be implemented through the immigration and emigration offices in Matara, Vavuniya and Kandy districts.",
        "Thus, he said, the current congestion in the main office in Colombo will be reduced.",
        "He also said that a separate counter will be opened to obtain passports under the one-day passport service for those who have the necessary documents to apply for a foreign job."
      ],
